{"lemma":"زُحَل","slug":"زُحَل","root":"ز.ح.ل","root_slug":"ز-ح-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ح-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["name","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17543","","n17547","n17548","n17550"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8F%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%84"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"name","gloss":"Saturn (planet)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to move away, withdraw, retire"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to remove"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of زَحَلَ (zaḥala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ز ح ل (z ḥ l) meaning \"to be distant or remote\", \"to linger away from others\"; so called as it is the furthest and has the slowest orbital period of the classical seven heavenly bodies (counting the Sun and the Moon, without the inclusion of Earth).\n\nCompare Hebrew זחל (zaħál, “crawl”)\n\nCausative of زَحَلَ (zaḥala, “to move away”)."},"ipa":["/zu.ħal/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17543","headword_ar":"زَحَلَ","root":"zHl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuHuwlN","text_ar":"زُحُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaHolN","text_ar":"زَحْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 125) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazoHalN","text_ar":"مَزْحَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed, withdrew,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retired to a distance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA, and Ham ubi suprà;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went back"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"backwards, drew back, receded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retreated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano makaAnihi","text_ar":"عَنْ مَكَانِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his place"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tzH~l","text_ar":"تزحّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) Hence, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AizoHalo Ean~iY faqado nazaHotaniY","text_ar":"اِزْحَلْ عَنِّى فَقَدْ نَزَحْتَنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Remove thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for thou hast exhausted me of what I possessed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazoHalu Eani AlA^amuwri","text_ar":"يَزْحَلُ عَنِ الاَمُورِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA, in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amori","text_ar":"الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removes, withdraws,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retires far away, from affairs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, distant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remote."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaHala","text_ar":"زَحَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano maqaAmihi","text_ar":"عَنْ مَقَامِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaHolN","text_ar":"زَحْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuHuwlN","text_ar":"زُحُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazoHalN","text_ar":"مَزْحَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quitted its station,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"standing-place;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazaHowala","text_ar":"تَزَحْوَلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) in some copies of the K, in the explanation of this phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zal~a","text_ar":"زَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAla","text_ar":"زَالَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaHalato","text_ar":"زَحَلَتْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"held back, hung back,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lagged behind, in her course,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaHala","text_ar":"زَحَلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, fatigued, tired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jaded."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n17547","headword_ar":"زَحِلٌ","root":"zHl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziHoliylN","text_ar":"زِحْلِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Removing, withdrawing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retiring to a distance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going back"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"backwards, drawing back, receding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retreating;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) from a place. (S, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17548","headword_ar":"زُحَلٌ","root":"zHl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who removes, withdraws,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retires far away, from affairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether they be good or evil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuHalu","text_ar":"زُحَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", imperfectly decl., (S, K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eumaru","text_ar":"عُمَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) because it is a proper name and deviates from the original form [which is app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~aAHilu","text_ar":"الزَّاحِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", reg. part. n. of 1], (Mbr, TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The planet Saturn;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain star, of those called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxun~asu","text_ar":"الخُنَّسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) so called because it is remote; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"said to be in the Seventh Heaven."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gulaAmu zuHala","text_ar":"غُلَامُ زُحَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The young man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slave, of Saturn"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is [a surname of] Abu-l-Kásim the well-known astronomer or astrologer. (K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","K","Mbr"]},{"entry_id":"n17550","headword_ar":"زِحَلٌّ","root":"zHl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that drives far away the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels, pressing against them so as to remove them, in the coming to water, and then drinks."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}